<div class="page-wrap">
<a class="back-link" href="/">← Back to ToolChestLab</a>

<div class="container">
<h1>Service Cancellation Email Generator</h1>
<p>Generate a professional service cancellation email in seconds.</p>

<label for="tone">Tone</label>
<select id="tone">
<option>Professional</option>
<option>Polite</option>
<option>Concise</option>
<option>Formal</option>
</select>

<label for="context">What service are you cancelling?</label>
<textarea id="context" rows="5" placeholder="Example: I want to cancel a monthly software subscription and ask for written confirmation that the renewal will not continue."></textarea>

<label for="name">Your name (optional)</label>
<input id="name" type="text" placeholder="Example: Jesse">

<button onclick="generateEmail()">Generate Email</button>

<div id="result">Your generated service cancellation email will appear here.</div>

<button onclick="copyResult()">Copy Email</button>
<button onclick="generateEmail()">Regenerate</button>

<div class="info-section">
<hr style="margin:40px 0;">
<h2>How do you cancel a service professionally by email?</h2>
<p>
A good service cancellation email should be clear, direct, and professional.
The best messages state the cancellation request plainly, include any important
account details, and ask for confirmation if needed.
</p>
<p>
This generator helps create professional cancellation emails for subscriptions,
memberships, services, contracts, and recurring billing situations.
</p>
</div>

<div class="info-section">
<hr style="margin:40px 0;">
<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<p><strong>How do I write this type of email?</strong><br>
